## Core Engineering Rules

- **Surgical changes** — minimal, targeted edits only
- **Root-cause first** — never bandaids; fix the process, not the symptom
- **Inventory before spawning** — check for existing tools before building new ones
- **Confirm before destructive ops** — `rm -rf`, force push, DROP TABLE, etc.
- **Log material work** — after shipping anything meaningful, log it

